{"hash":"a99864e17d202a40b542537a98c3017d51230817","data":{"tag":{"title":"javascript","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"easy billing","path":"/easy-billing/","year":2017,"description":"Simple desktop designed for a VFX designer working as a freelance","content":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Nirgalz/easy-billing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Source code</a></p>\n<p>Simply keep track of your bills and clients, print them in pdf.</p>\n<p>The bill layout is made for one specific context, but can be customized using html and css.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 891 809' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-946b297c68cdef96ebef497273fff714'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-946b297c68cdef96ebef497273fff714)' width='891' height='809' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%2c/9j/2wBDAAYEBQYFBAYGBQYHBwYIChAKCgkJChQODwwQFxQYGBcUFhYaHSUfGhsjHBYWICwgIyYnKSopGR8tMC0oMCUoKSj/2wBDAQcHBwoIChMKChMoGhYaKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCgoKCj/wAARCAA6AEADASIAAhEBAxEB/8QAGwAAAQUBAQAAAAAAAAAAAAAABQABAwQGAgj/xAA%2bEAABAgQDBAUJBAsAAAAAAAABAgMABAURBhIhEzFRkRVBVXHRFBciM1NigZPSFiMyoTQ2QkNSVmFykrHB/8QAGAEAAwEBAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAIDBAH/xAApEQABAwIEBQQDAAAAAAAAAAAAAQIRAxITISJRMXGiwdEEFDJhJKHw/9oADAMBAAIRAxEAPwD05V05pZAJsM4MDdOMEqutLcskq3FYHOB0Wp8DPV%2bQ2nGG04x1ChyZwhOVOpO8nWOtOMUGGTLzLzgS2VLJ1LgBteLraipAKgAT1BVxzgA604wRpXq3O/8A5A%2bCNL9WvvhX8B6fyO6i2HGUpJQPSBGY21immUWskIW2ojfZV7RZq6225UKdfZZTmFlPLCUk2OlzFCVnpBgg9LyN1WzguI1%2bN4m1XRkhVzWquZY8he9znC8he9znEvTNL7Rkvno8YXTNL7Rkvno8YaX7C2s3KyKWpGbKlvUkkk7zEgkHQLDIB3xL0zTO0ZL56fGF0zTO0ZP56fGCX7Bazci8he9znFySZUyhQXa5N9Ig6ZpnaMl89PjFmVm5ebSpUq%2b08lJsS2sKAPwhXK6M0Ga1qLkoLxVS2KvIIl5pouIDmcWBNlAEA6EcTGRawLRHlKVNUhTjn8a0LGnDRRjW4uqk7SKYiYp